sequenceDiagram
    actor Superuser
    participant Browser
    participant Django as Django (accounts views)
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Email as Email Backend

    %% ── List users ──────────────────────────────────────────────
    Superuser->>Browser: Navigate to /accounts/users/
    Browser->>Django: GET /accounts/users/?active=&q=
    Django->>Django: @user_passes_test(is_superuser) check
    alt Not superuser
        Django-->>Browser: 403 Forbidden
    end
    Django->>DB: User.objects.all() with optional filter (active/inactive, search)
    DB-->>Django: QuerySet[User]
    Django-->>Browser: 200 accounts/user_list.html\n(table: email, date joined, active, last login)

    %% ── Activate / deactivate ────────────────────────────────────
    Superuser->>Browser: Click toggle on a user row
    Browser->>Django: POST /accounts/users/<id>/toggle-active/\n(HX-Request header)
    Django->>Django: @user_passes_test(is_superuser) check
    Django->>DB: user.is_active = not user.is_active user.save()
    DB-->>Django: OK
    Django-->>Browser: 200 partial accounts/partials/user_row.html\n(HTMX swaps the row in-place)

    %% ── Reset password ───────────────────────────────────────────
    Superuser->>Browser: Click "Send Reset Email" for a user
    Browser->>Django: POST /accounts/users/<id>/reset-password/
    Django->>Django: @user_passes_test(is_superuser) check
    Django->>DB: Fetch User by id
    DB-->>Django: User
    Django->>Django: Build PasswordResetForm for that email\nand call form.save() to trigger email
    Django->>Email: Send password_reset.txt to user.email\n(same template as self-service reset)
    Email-->>Django: OK
    Django-->>Browser: 200 HX-Redirect or flash message\n("Reset email sent to <email>")

    %% ── Filter by active status ──────────────────────────────────
    Superuser->>Browser: Select "Inactive" in filter dropdown
    Browser->>Django: GET /accounts/users/?active=false\n(HTMX partial table refresh)
    Django->>DB: User.objects.filter(is_active=False)
    DB-->>Django: QuerySet[User]
    Django-->>Browser: 200 accounts/partials/user_table.html\n(HTMX swaps table body)
